00:25:57,710 --> 00:25:59,660
Wait, what bed did you say she was on?

542
00:25:59,710 --> 00:26:00,680
Mine.

543
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:02,760
I'm sure I put her on my bed.

544
00:26:02,810 --> 00:26:04,700
No, she was definitely on my bed.

545
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:07,050
