547
00:26:09,930 --> 00:26:11,710
Oh, oh, oh...

548
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,470
No! No! No!

549
00:26:15,780 --> 00:26:17,110
Yes!

550
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:20,340
You were under the pile of coats?

551
00:26:20,390 --> 00:26:22,800
I was the pile of coats!

552
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,670
Oh, my God!

553
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,990
You were my midnight mystery kisser?!

554
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:36,180
You were my first kiss with Rachel?!

555
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:39,860
You were my first kiss ever?!

556
00:26:42,420 --> 00:26:44,650
What did I marry into?!

557
00:27:19,450 --> 00:27:21,030
Crap!

